1
00:00:09,009 --> 00:00:11,428
PUSAT RAWATAN KECEMASAN

2
00:00:18,935 --> 00:00:20,311
Tolong bagi sedatif.

3
00:00:20,395 --> 00:00:21,312
Macam mana ini?

4
00:00:21,396 --> 00:00:22,480
Bawa bertenang.

5
00:00:22,564 --> 00:00:23,815
Mak saya sakit.

6
00:00:23,898 --> 00:00:24,858
Berapa lama?

7
00:00:25,692 --> 00:00:27,402
Dia tak boleh tidur semalam.

8
00:00:27,944 --> 00:00:30,405
Kami akan rawat dia. Tolong tunggu.

9
00:00:31,740 --> 00:00:34,200
Tolong beri laluan.

10
00:00:37,829 --> 00:00:40,081
Doktor, tolonglah…

11
00:00:40,165 --> 00:00:43,001
Tolong beri laluan.

12
00:00:43,084 --> 00:00:46,546
Awak perlu berjaga. Buka mata. Encik!

13
00:01:10,153 --> 00:01:11,780
- Terima kasih.
- Sama-sama.

14
00:01:18,870 --> 00:01:19,704
Mak.

15
00:01:20,830 --> 00:01:21,664
Apa?

16
00:01:28,880 --> 00:01:30,006
Aduhai…

17
00:01:36,221 --> 00:01:37,555
Maafkan mak.

18
00:01:45,772 --> 00:01:46,606
Jom.

19
00:02:27,355 --> 00:02:30,733
BLOODHOUNDS

20
00:02:32,152 --> 00:02:34,112
- En. An Mun-ju?
- Ya.

21
00:02:40,160 --> 00:02:42,579
Awak bernasib baik tiada kerosakan saraf.

22
00:02:43,872 --> 00:02:45,415
Awak tak nak padam parut?

23
00:02:46,416 --> 00:02:48,626
Rawatan ini hanya untuk tutup luka,

24
00:02:48,710 --> 00:02:52,422
tapi awak perlu terima
rawatan segera agar tak berparut.

25
00:02:52,505 --> 00:02:53,590
Mahal, bukan?

26
00:02:53,673 --> 00:02:55,425
Saya boleh syorkan awak.

27
00:02:56,342 --> 00:02:59,679
Ini gambar rawatan
yang dibuat baru-baru ini.

28
00:03:00,180 --> 00:03:01,973
Nampak parut di dahi dia?

29
00:03:02,056 --> 00:03:02,891
Ya.

30
00:03:02,974 --> 00:03:04,726
Ini gambar sebelum rawatan.

31
00:03:05,268 --> 00:03:07,437
Ini pula selepas rawatan laser.

32
00:03:07,520 --> 00:03:08,396
Ya.

33
00:03:08,479 --> 00:03:10,773
Parut itu di muka dan awak masih muda.

34
00:03:10,857 --> 00:03:13,568
Saya fikir eloklah awak buat rawatan.

35
00:03:15,570 --> 00:03:17,655
Tak apalah. Terima kasih.

36
00:03:19,532 --> 00:03:21,492
Encik Choi Han-seon?

37
00:03:22,493 --> 00:03:23,703
Ya, silakan.

38
00:03:23,786 --> 00:03:24,621
Woo-jin.

39
00:03:28,833 --> 00:03:29,667
Awak okey?

40
00:03:31,294 --> 00:03:32,921
- Biar saya tengok.
- Usah.

41
00:03:33,630 --> 00:03:34,589
Tunjuklah.

42
00:03:42,096 --> 00:03:43,348
Aduhai.

43
00:03:47,018 --> 00:03:48,269
Berapa jahitan?

44
00:03:49,187 --> 00:03:50,146
Tiga puluh.

45
00:03:50,730 --> 00:03:54,025
Jahanam betul. Mereka buat saya bengang.

46
00:03:56,194 --> 00:03:57,028
Kita laporkan.

47
00:03:59,489 --> 00:04:02,325
Jika awak buat laporan, mak awak mati.

48
00:04:08,164 --> 00:04:10,083
- Tak boleh.
- Kenapa?

49
00:04:10,166 --> 00:04:11,834
Ia boleh bahayakan mak saya.

50
00:04:13,711 --> 00:04:15,171
Jahanam.

51
00:04:15,964 --> 00:04:17,548
Sudah baca kontrak?

52
00:04:19,342 --> 00:04:20,176
Sudah.

53
00:04:20,677 --> 00:04:21,511
Tengok ini.

54
00:04:22,220 --> 00:04:25,098
Saya tak pernah dengar
tentang "bayaran penangguhan".

55
00:04:25,181 --> 00:04:26,474
Bayaran 10 peratus

56
00:04:26,557 --> 00:04:29,477
daripada jumlah pokok setiap minggu
sehingga hutang langsai.

57
00:04:29,560 --> 00:04:32,563
Mak cik kena bayar lima juta won
untuk pinjaman 50 juta.

58
00:04:33,064 --> 00:04:35,358
Tapi jika tak bayar, ia digandakan.

59
00:04:35,441 --> 00:04:37,443
Kadar faedah juga jadi 20 peratus.

60
00:04:37,944 --> 00:04:41,114
Ia ditulis dengan halus
supaya orang tak perasan.

61
00:04:41,197 --> 00:04:43,574
Ini penipuan. Mak awak terpedaya.

62
00:04:44,075 --> 00:04:45,076
Jadi, macam mana?

63
00:04:45,159 --> 00:04:47,078
Awak kena bayar secepat mungkin.

64
00:04:47,161 --> 00:04:49,455
Ia akan jadi 100 juta.
Rumah awak dah dicagarkan.

65
00:04:50,790 --> 00:04:51,749
Kami tiada duit.

66
00:04:53,543 --> 00:04:56,296
Cis, habislah.

67
00:05:03,219 --> 00:05:04,178
Jom makan.

68
00:05:04,262 --> 00:05:06,180
Saya belanja. Nak makan apa?

69
00:05:09,434 --> 00:05:10,393
Mata rusuk.

70
00:05:11,477 --> 00:05:13,688
Awak masih boleh bergurau?

71
00:05:14,355 --> 00:05:15,773
Saya teringin sangat.

72
00:05:16,983 --> 00:05:17,859
Okey.

73
00:05:19,068 --> 00:05:21,738
Saya belanja lauk daging
sesedap mata rusuk.

74
00:05:23,823 --> 00:05:24,741
Tak apalah.

75
00:05:27,160 --> 00:05:29,329
Saya selalu ke sini selepas latihan.

76
00:05:29,412 --> 00:05:31,331
Ini rutin saya. Wajib buat.

77
00:05:31,414 --> 00:05:34,459
Jangan merungut dan cuba rasa dulu, okey?

78
00:05:34,542 --> 00:05:37,086
- Okey.
- Mak cik!

79
00:05:37,170 --> 00:05:39,213
Awak rupanya.

80
00:05:39,297 --> 00:05:40,923
- Aduhai.
- Dua jeyuk bokkeum.

81
00:05:41,007 --> 00:05:42,967
Boleh. Awak bawa kawan.

82
00:05:43,051 --> 00:05:44,719
- Helo.
- Kawan tinju saya.

83
00:05:44,802 --> 00:05:46,179
Begitu.

84
00:05:51,893 --> 00:05:53,853
- Saya jawab panggilan.
- Okey.

85
00:05:54,645 --> 00:05:55,563
Helo.

86
00:05:55,646 --> 00:05:58,691
Saya Woo-jin. Apa khabar?

87
00:05:59,901 --> 00:06:01,486
Sebenarnya begini…

88
00:06:08,368 --> 00:06:09,952
ANAK MAK

89
00:06:11,454 --> 00:06:12,497
Gun-woo.

90
00:06:13,081 --> 00:06:14,916
Woo-jin dah baca kontrak itu.

91
00:06:14,999 --> 00:06:17,877
Mereka penipu profesional.
Ia tak boleh dielak.

92
00:06:18,628 --> 00:06:20,046
Bukan salah mak.

93
00:06:20,129 --> 00:06:21,714
Terima kasih, nak.

94
00:06:23,299 --> 00:06:25,968
Bagaimana dengan kecederaan awak?

95
00:06:26,719 --> 00:06:28,388
Ia pulih dengan elok.

96
00:06:28,930 --> 00:06:30,264
Syukurlah.

97
00:06:31,349 --> 00:06:33,518
Saya dan Woo-jin akan kemas kafe.

98
00:06:33,601 --> 00:06:35,520
Mak berehatlah di rumah.

99
00:06:37,021 --> 00:06:40,608
Usah. Mak akan kemas. Biarkan sahajalah.

100
00:06:40,691 --> 00:06:43,653
Tak apa. Saya akan kemas
sebelum balik. Okey?

101
00:06:43,736 --> 00:06:45,238
Pesanan awak dah siap.

102
00:06:48,658 --> 00:06:51,869
Mak, saya akan telefon waktu pulang nanti.

103
00:06:51,953 --> 00:06:53,788
- Okey.
- Okey.

104
00:07:00,086 --> 00:07:02,964
Tolonglah saya sekali ini sahaja.

105
00:07:03,047 --> 00:07:05,049
Bukan saya, tapi kawan saya.

106
00:07:05,842 --> 00:07:08,928
Saya takkan tangguh
bayaran duit pokok dan bunga.

107
00:07:10,096 --> 00:07:13,391
Kami perlu bayar
kadar bunga tinggi di tempat lain.

108
00:07:13,891 --> 00:07:15,726
Berilah kadar lebih rendah.

109
00:07:15,810 --> 00:07:17,937
Tolonglah saya. Sekali sahaja.

110
00:07:18,521 --> 00:07:20,523
Dia kawan baik saya.

111
00:07:22,024 --> 00:07:23,192
Tolonglah.

112
00:07:23,276 --> 00:07:25,319
Saya kutip banyak hutang awak.

113
00:07:26,320 --> 00:07:28,114
Saya tak minta apa-apa pun.

114
00:07:58,019 --> 00:07:59,979
Kenapa tak panggil?

115
00:08:00,062 --> 00:08:01,647
Baru sahaja siap.

116
00:08:02,523 --> 00:08:03,524
Makanlah.

117
00:08:03,608 --> 00:08:06,068
Ini jeyuk bokkeum tersedap dalam negara.

118
00:08:12,950 --> 00:08:14,619
- Betul? Makanlah.
- Ya.

119
00:08:26,172 --> 00:08:28,925
KITA BINCANG DI PEJABAT

120
00:08:29,008 --> 00:08:32,303
Dia agak panas baran.
Diam dan dengar sahaja.

121
00:08:32,803 --> 00:08:34,138
Biar saya uruskan.

122
00:08:34,222 --> 00:08:35,056
Okey.

123
00:08:37,767 --> 00:08:39,560
- En. Seo.
- Ya.

124
00:08:39,644 --> 00:08:41,020
Berapa harganya?

125
00:08:41,562 --> 00:08:43,231
Lebih kurang 20 juta won.

126
00:08:43,314 --> 00:08:44,148
Bos!

127
00:08:44,732 --> 00:08:45,942
Saya dah sampai.

128
00:08:47,401 --> 00:08:48,361
Hei, celaka.

129
00:08:48,444 --> 00:08:49,904
Bertahun menghilang,

130
00:08:49,987 --> 00:08:52,073
tiba-tiba muncul nak pinjam duit?

131
00:08:52,156 --> 00:08:54,575
Kau ingat aku bank?

132
00:08:55,076 --> 00:08:56,911
- Maaf, bos.
- Sudahlah.

133
00:08:56,994 --> 00:08:58,037
Relakslah.

134
00:08:58,120 --> 00:09:00,164
Jahanam.

135
00:09:01,040 --> 00:09:02,333
- Duduk.
- Mari duduk.

136
00:09:02,416 --> 00:09:03,251
Okey.

137
00:09:08,464 --> 00:09:11,551
Apa dia buat sampai berhutang?

138
00:09:12,134 --> 00:09:14,637
Kena tipu samseng. Smile Capital.

139
00:09:15,221 --> 00:09:18,057
Smile Capital? Mereka dari Gwangan-dong?

140
00:09:18,683 --> 00:09:20,101
Saya tak tahu lokasinya.

141
00:09:20,851 --> 00:09:22,228
Ceh.

142
00:09:23,145 --> 00:09:26,023
Hei, Smile Capital
bukan sebarangan samseng.

143
00:09:26,107 --> 00:09:27,441
Mereka syarikat besar.

144
00:09:28,109 --> 00:09:28,943
Berapa?

145
00:09:29,944 --> 00:09:30,820
Sejuta won.

146
00:09:35,908 --> 00:09:37,076
Habislah.

147
00:09:37,159 --> 00:09:39,078
Tolonglah kami, bos.

148
00:09:39,161 --> 00:09:40,580
Awak banyak duit.

149
00:09:44,166 --> 00:09:46,752
Saya beri pinjaman 100 juta,
bunga rendah setahun.

150
00:09:49,505 --> 00:09:51,048
Terima kasih, bos.

151
00:09:53,134 --> 00:09:55,678
Tapi kau kena bekerja dengan aku semula.

152
00:09:56,679 --> 00:09:58,848
Kerja ini maju sebab COVID-19.

153
00:09:58,931 --> 00:10:01,183
Kita guna peluang ini untuk buat duit.

154
00:10:01,767 --> 00:10:03,060
Tolonglah.

155
00:10:03,144 --> 00:10:06,480
Aku akan bagi bonus lumayan
untuk setiap kutipan.

156
00:10:08,149 --> 00:10:10,443
Alamak, ini mengejut.

157
00:10:10,526 --> 00:10:11,652
Cis.

158
00:10:11,736 --> 00:10:14,155
Jadi pengutip hutang aku setahun.

159
00:10:15,072 --> 00:10:17,283
Hei, ini peluang baik.

160
00:10:17,366 --> 00:10:19,827
Kau boleh dapat duit banyak.

161
00:10:20,328 --> 00:10:22,038
Bila lagi boleh dapat duit banyak?

162
00:10:22,997 --> 00:10:26,500
Saya faham, tapi ini terlalu mengejut…

163
00:10:27,627 --> 00:10:29,462
- Buat keputusan.
- Jom.

164
00:10:31,213 --> 00:10:32,048
Apa?

165
00:10:32,131 --> 00:10:34,383
Kerja ini kena belasah orang?

166
00:10:36,469 --> 00:10:39,055
Belasah orang untuk duit,
itu kerja samseng.

167
00:10:40,473 --> 00:10:41,390
Kita petinju.

168
00:10:44,018 --> 00:10:44,977
Hei, budak.

169
00:10:45,645 --> 00:10:48,564
Jika gagal bayar Smile Capital,
kau akan mati.

170
00:10:48,648 --> 00:10:50,274
Mereka ambil organ sekali.

171
00:11:02,536 --> 00:11:03,579
Apa ini?

172
00:11:03,663 --> 00:11:06,499
Terima kasih banyak.
Saya datang lain kali.

173
00:11:08,209 --> 00:11:09,043
Hei, jom.

174
00:11:09,835 --> 00:11:11,504
Celaka, kau ingat ini lawak?

175
00:11:14,048 --> 00:11:15,007
Kelakarkah?

176
00:11:24,725 --> 00:11:26,018
Saya bergurau sahaja.

177
00:11:27,520 --> 00:11:28,688
Jumpa lagi.

178
00:11:31,524 --> 00:11:32,400
Jom.

179
00:11:35,903 --> 00:11:37,905
Celaka.

180
00:11:39,365 --> 00:11:40,366
Hei, petinju.

181
00:11:47,039 --> 00:11:48,874
- Turunkan cap.
- Okey.

182
00:11:50,167 --> 00:11:53,462
Selepas perniagaan awak maju,
kami nak bahagian kami.

183
00:11:53,546 --> 00:11:56,132
Terima kasih banyak.

184
00:12:01,470 --> 00:12:02,930
- Syabas.
- Jom.

185
00:13:11,373 --> 00:13:12,458
Semua okey?

186
00:13:13,459 --> 00:13:14,627
Ya.

187
00:13:15,127 --> 00:13:17,338
Oh, ya. Ini.

188
00:13:17,421 --> 00:13:19,590
Duit yang dikumpul hari ini.

189
00:13:20,966 --> 00:13:25,179
Kami sedang kumpul
kad pengenalan gelandangan.

190
00:13:25,679 --> 00:13:27,181
Cik ini siapa?

191
00:13:27,264 --> 00:13:29,433
Tengok apa? Sambung kerja awak.

192
00:13:29,517 --> 00:13:30,434
Okey.

193
00:13:31,894 --> 00:13:34,063
Kami akan usahakan agar awak dapat

194
00:13:34,146 --> 00:13:36,524
jumlah yang diperlukan secepat mungkin.

195
00:13:39,693 --> 00:13:41,237
Boleh sudahkan minggu ini?

196
00:13:41,320 --> 00:13:43,322
Minggu ini? Saya akan cuba.

197
00:13:43,405 --> 00:13:46,075
KIM JUN-MIN

198
00:13:49,870 --> 00:13:51,664
PELITUP MUKA WAJIB DIPAKAI
DI BILIK MENUNGGU

199
00:13:56,544 --> 00:13:59,713
Aduhai, maaf buat kamu menunggu.

200
00:13:59,797 --> 00:14:02,591
DREAM ON CAPITAL

201
00:14:02,675 --> 00:14:04,760
Kenapa tak pakai pelitup muka?

202
00:14:05,511 --> 00:14:06,345
Saya akan pakai.

203
00:14:06,428 --> 00:14:10,182
Saya tanya sebab awak tak pakai,
bukan suruh awak pakai semula.

204
00:14:10,266 --> 00:14:12,434
Kami dah tunggu lebih 30 minit.

205
00:14:12,518 --> 00:14:13,519
Saya rasa rimas.

206
00:14:13,602 --> 00:14:14,812
Hei!

207
00:14:14,895 --> 00:14:17,523
Macam mana nak lindungi orang
jika tak sabar?

208
00:14:17,606 --> 00:14:20,818
Apa kaitan pelitup muka
dengan melindungi orang?

209
00:14:20,901 --> 00:14:21,735
Keluar.

210
00:14:22,945 --> 00:14:23,779
Berambus!

211
00:14:26,073 --> 00:14:26,949
Cis.

212
00:14:29,410 --> 00:14:31,036
Bedebah…

213
00:14:32,663 --> 00:14:34,248
Tak guna.

214
00:14:35,749 --> 00:14:38,002
- Awak pun sama, bukan?
- Tak.

215
00:14:38,085 --> 00:14:38,919
Saya nampak.

216
00:14:39,503 --> 00:14:40,796
Saya cuma turunkannya.

217
00:14:40,880 --> 00:14:43,299
Sama sahaja. Jangan beri alasan, pengecut.

218
00:14:43,382 --> 00:14:44,258
Keluar.

219
00:14:45,301 --> 00:14:46,135
Berambus!

220
00:14:46,218 --> 00:14:47,928
Celaka.

221
00:14:49,305 --> 00:14:51,307
Apa? "Celaka"?

222
00:14:51,807 --> 00:14:53,893
"Celaka"?

223
00:14:53,976 --> 00:14:55,394
Jahanam.

224
00:14:58,606 --> 00:14:59,648
Buka pelitup muka.

225
00:15:03,777 --> 00:15:05,112
Apa nama awak?

226
00:15:05,696 --> 00:15:06,780
Cheon Dong-woo.

227
00:15:06,864 --> 00:15:08,198
Ketinggian awak?

228
00:15:08,282 --> 00:15:10,242
Tinggi 187 sm, berat 74 kg.

229
00:15:10,910 --> 00:15:11,869
Awak bersukan?

230
00:15:11,952 --> 00:15:14,288
Tinju dan hapkido selama sepuluh tahun.

231
00:15:14,872 --> 00:15:15,873
Jurusan apa?

232
00:15:15,956 --> 00:15:17,499
Khidmat Keselamatan di Yongheon.

233
00:15:20,294 --> 00:15:23,255
Wah, awak graduan elit.

234
00:15:23,339 --> 00:15:24,298
Khidmat negara?

235
00:15:24,381 --> 00:15:25,299
Saya dikecualikan.

236
00:15:26,425 --> 00:15:28,260
Saya cedera ketika bermain bola tampar.

237
00:15:29,428 --> 00:15:30,262
Begitu.

238
00:15:32,014 --> 00:15:32,848
Lain kali sahaja.

239
00:15:32,932 --> 00:15:34,767
Boleh saya tahu sebabnya?

240
00:15:35,517 --> 00:15:36,727
Saya cari tentera marin.

241
00:15:36,810 --> 00:15:38,228
Itu syarat wajib?

242
00:15:38,312 --> 00:15:40,147
Ya.

243
00:15:40,648 --> 00:15:44,193
Tak guna. Kalau begitu,
awak patut nyatakan dalam iklan.

244
00:15:44,276 --> 00:15:46,362
Tunggu. "Tak guna"?

245
00:15:46,445 --> 00:15:48,447
Awak buang masa saya!

246
00:15:48,530 --> 00:15:50,991
Jaga adab di depan orang lebih tua.

247
00:15:51,075 --> 00:15:52,284
Saya tak peduli.

248
00:15:52,368 --> 00:15:54,578
Kalau lebih tua, awak tak boleh…

249
00:15:58,374 --> 00:16:00,167
Lain kali sahaja, okey?

250
00:16:00,751 --> 00:16:01,585
Baiklah!

251
00:16:04,129 --> 00:16:07,049
TENTERA MARIN
JIKA TAK BOLEH, USAHAKAN!

252
