316
00:19:38,385 --> 00:19:41,430
Tak perlu. Kami boleh uruskan.

317
00:19:41,513 --> 00:19:43,682
Itu kepakaran En. Oh.

318
00:19:44,266 --> 00:19:45,392
Okey.

319
00:19:45,475 --> 00:19:50,189
Mari jumpa dan makan
di kedai Yang-jung. Okey.

320
00:19:53,275 --> 00:19:56,528
Yang Jae-myeong ke Chungjeong-ro
dan Myeong-dong

321
00:19:56,612 --> 00:19:59,573
